<hr><a name="_details"></a><h2>Detailed Description</h2>
The adjust bar widget consists of a title, a caption, a ruler and a knob. 
<p>
The knob can be moved in the range of the ruler, while the position (which is represented by the caption of the widget) is scaled from <em>ruler width</em> to <em>range</em>, which means it is always a value from 0 to <em>range</em>.<hr><h2>Function Documentation</h2>
